quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  54,41,Kandi rwose kuburira (kwanjye) kwageze ku bantu ba Farawo
  54,42,"Bahinyuye ibitangaza byacu byose, nuko turabafata tubahanisha ibihano by’Umunyembaraga uhebuje, Ushobora byose"
  54,43,"Ese abahakanyi banyu (b’i Maka) ni bo beza kurusha abo (abantu ba Adi, aba Thamudi, aba Nuhu n’aba Farawo, boretswe)? Cyangwa mufite ubudahangarwa bwanditse mu bitabo (bwo kutazahanwa)"
  54,44,"Cyangwa (abo bahakanyi) baravuga bati \"Twe turi benshi bashyize hamwe, bashoboye kwitabara"
  54,45,Nyamara abo bishyize hamwe bazatsindwa banayabangire ingata
  54,46,"Ahubwo umunsi w’imperuka ni cyo gihe basezeranyijwe (cyo kuzahanirwaho), ndetse imperuka izaba iteye ubwoba cyane kandi irura"
  54,47,"Mu by’ ukuri, inkozi z’ibibi ziri mu buyobe (hano ku isi) kandi zizahanishwa umuriro utwika"
  54,48,"Umunsi uburanga bwabo buzakururirwa mu muriro (bazabwirwa bati) \"Ngaho nimusogongere igihano cy’umuriro"
  54,49,"Mu by’ukuri, buri kintu twakiremeye igeno ryacyo"
  54,50,Kandi itegeko ryacu ni ijambo rimwe; (ryihuta) nko guhumbya no guhumbura
  54,51,Kandi rwose tworetse abantu bameze nkamwe (mu buhakanyi). Ese hari uwibuka (ngo bimugirire akamaro)
  54,52,Kandi buri kintu cyose bakoze cyanditswe mu bitabo (by’ibikorwa byabo)
  54,53,"Na buri kintu, cyaba gito cyangwa kinini, kiranditse"
  54,54,"Mu by’ukuri, abatinya Allah bazaba bari mu busitani n’imigezi (Ijuru)"
  54,55,"Mu byicaro by’ukuri, hafi y’Umwami ushobora byose"